<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= character.name %>와 추리 대화</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="chat-body">
    <header class="chat-header" style="--accent:<%= character.accentColor %>;">
      <a class="back-link" href="/">← 캐릭터 선택으로 돌아가기</a>
      <div>
        <p class="chat-label">비밀을 간직한 친구</p>
        <h1><%= character.name %>와 대화하기</h1>
        <p><%= character.greeting %></p>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main class="chat-shell">
      <aside class="character-panel">
        <h2>궁금해볼 단서</h2>
        <p class="panel-hint">질문을 던져서 직접 단서를 찾아보세요!</p>
        <h3>추천 질문</h3>
        <div class="suggestion-list" id="suggestions"></div>
      </aside>
      <section class="chat-window">
        <div id="chat-log" class="chat-log">
          <div class="bubble bubble-assistant highlight">
            안녕! 나는 <%= character.name %>야. 아직 어디 사는지 말할 수는 없지만,
            질문을 잘하면 금방 알아맞힐 수 있을 거야!
          </div>
        </div>
        <form id="chat-form" class="chat-form">
          <input
            id="chat-input"
            name="message"
            type="text"
            placeholder="단서를 얻기 위한 질문을 적어보세요"
            autocomplete="off"
            required
          />
          <button type="submit">전송</button>
        </form>
      </section>
    </main>
    <section class="note-section">
      <div class="note-card">
        <h3>나만의 단서 노트</h3>
        <textarea class="note-area" aria-label="단서 메모 공간"></textarea>
      </div>
    </section>
    <script>
      window.__CHARACTER__ = {
        id: '<%= characterId %>',
        starterQuestions: <%- JSON.stringify(character.starterQuestions) %>,
      };
    </script>
    <script src="/chat.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
